text: Jermaine Anthony Preyan (born July 28, 1982), better known by his stage name Mack Maine, is an American rapper, songwriter and record executive. Maine has been the president of Young Money Entertainment since 2009. He is also signed to Cash Money Records, Republic Records, Soothe Your Soul and Kush Entertainment. Maine has collaborated with Lil Wayne and others.
